title: Sefton Council Joint Strategic Needs Assessment (JSNA)
lead: The Joint Strategic Needs Assessment (JSNA) looks at the current and future health and care needs of the local population to inform and guide the planning and commissioning (development of services) of health, etc.
content: The Joint Strategic Needs Assessment (JSNA) looks at the current and future health and care needs of the local population to inform and guide the planning and commissioning (development of services) of health, well-being and social care services within the Sefton authority area.
